Detailed_Description:
Add an Artist to the figure.  Usually artists are added to axes objects using Axes.add_artist ;
this method can be used in the rare cases where one needs to add
artists directly to the figure instead.

Example:
{
'markerfacecolor'
:
{
'mfc'
},
'linewidth'
:
{
'lw'
},
}
